<div class="col-md-5"> <div class="person_img"> <img src="img/3 (9).png" alt="Bhavana Chamoli"> <a class="download_btn" href="#"><span>Download Resume</span></a> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-7"> <div class="row person_details"> <h3>An Autodidact with a Passion for Lifelong Learning and Personal Growth, an artist and a scientist</h3> <p class="text-justify">My curiosity and love for exploring new ideas have driven me to pursue various fields of study, including computer science, data analytics, and finance. I have gained extensive knowledge and skills in both traditional and emerging tech areas, such as - machine learning, statistical analysis, software technologies, and financial markets and investments. I am constantly seeking to expand my horizons and challenge myself to think beyond the conventional boundaries of my field.</p> <p class="text-justify">My interest in AI and machine learning was initially sparked by my study of information theory and design, and my admiration for great authors such as George Lanza. Their work taught me the significance of information in shaping our perception of the world. Through further research, particularly as presented by Henry Kissinger and Eric Schmidt, I have come to appreciate the vast potential of AI and machine learning. My observations and experiments in these fields have led me to explore new applications for this technology, including the use of adversarial models and other advanced techniques.</p> <p class="text-justify">In my free time, I continue to explore the latest ideas and techniques in AI and machine learning, constantly pushing the boundaries of what is possible. I would have said a year earlier that my goal is to leverage my expertise to solve real-world problems and to help others better understand the transformative potential of AI and machine learning. But to be more accurate and precise, I stand for ETHICAL AI.</p> <p><a class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" style="margin-top:10px;">Read More</a></p> <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">×</span></button> <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Bhavana Chamoli</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>Working in MIO Partners, Inc. at the position of Developer, Investment Research and Trading in New York, Bhavana Chamoli is an enthusiast and positive person. She has her interests in topics such as arts and culture, economic empowerment, human rights and science and technology. A fast-learner and talented personality, she is the Founder and President of the Indian Organisation. It works for civil rights and social actions in society. She has also been a volunteer as the Youth Development Specialist in AIESEC and worked for economic empowerment.</p> <p>Bhavana possesses excellent leadership and guidance qualities. She studied at the All Saint Convent School where she was the school leader and the student representative. Also, she was the gold medalist at the school. She has always been into extra-curricular activities alongside her studies. During her studies at Delhi public school, she had active participation in the debate competition. Moreover, she has been a member of the school’s Fine Arts Club            <ul class="social_icon">
